label("A",(5,10),N);
label("B",(5,0),S);
[/asy] The final Answer is 16
 ### Proof
 Draw a line segment from $A$ to $B,$ cutting the shaded diamond region in half. Next, draw the altitude from point $E$ to segment $AB.$ The new figure is shown below: [asy] draw((0,0)--(10,0)); draw((10,0)--(10,10));
